summary: This mod adds two terraces to Blue Palace, they offer new views and attempt to make Blue Palace more regal. This is part of Solitude modular expansions
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds two terraces to Blue Palace, they offer new views and attempt to make Blue Palace more regal. This is part of Solitude modular expansion.

First terrace is accesible from Jarl's chambers and is a peacefull reatreat with view toawrds center of the town.

Second terrace is northbound and covered in ice, rarely visited by anyone is a place of real solitude.
author: Ignatius Artemisius
